{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |category = Unique Monster |name = King Krawkin |image = XC3 King Krawkin.png |caption = King Krawkin |type = [[Tirkin]] |level = 102 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Demihuman Gutter]]) |spawntime = Anytime |respawn = Yes |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 5,383 |cp = 421 |sp = 5 |gold = 5,544 |hp = 3,643,200 |strength = 3,348 |healing = 1,355 |dexterity = 462 |agility = 290 |physdef = 0% |ethdef = 30% |critrate = 15% |guardrate-front = 20% |guardrate-side = 0% |guardrate-back = 100% }} '''King Krawkin''' is a [[Unique Monster (XC3)|Unique Monster]] in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Tirkin]] family, and can be found at level 102 in the [[Demihuman Gutter]] in [[Erythia Sea]]. It forms the duo "The King-Kings" with [[Conqueror Deepwan]]. The [[Desperate Charge]] [[Battle Arts (XC3)|Art]] can be earned by the [[Soulhacker]] [[Class (XC3)|class]] upon defeating it. {{clr}} == Resistances == {{XC3 Resistances |break = 75% |blowdown = 50% |knockback = 50% |physdebuff = 50% |etherdebuff = Immune }} {{clr}}
