{{for|other uses|Knockback}}
[[File:XC3 Knockback.png|thumb]]
'''Knockback''' is a reaction status in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. It pushes targets away from the attacker, interrupting their current attack and preventing them from attacking while they regain balance. It can be inflicted by certain [[Battle Arts (XC3)|Battle Arts]] and by some enemy attacks.

Certain enemies have resistance or immunity to the status.

